Title: Endless Horizons
Actors: Gisèle Pascal, Jean Chevrier, René Blancard, Paul Frankeur
Plot: Helene Boucher was one of the most famous French female pilots:she became for a while the fastest pilot in the world.A sales assistant ,she spent her free time learning all about the planes.Unfortunately her career would be short-lived : three years.After ceaseless efforts and an exclusive passion for flying ,she crashed on the ground:she was only twenty-six.
